Western Tele-CommunicationsInc said it plans to periodically repurchase shares of itsclass A and class B stock.    The company said it will repurchase an indeterminate amountof shares from institutional investors on the open market.    It said it expects to buy the shares using available fundswhen it believes the market prices of the stock issues are toolow.    Western said it plans to continue the program indefinitely. Reuter&#3;